te><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/reactions-japans-pm-kishida-stepping-down-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰降息，亚洲股市上涨，新西兰股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-14/</link><description>周三，美国生产者价格数据疲软，激发了消费者价格通胀温和的希望，导致债券收益率走低，亚洲股市上涨，美元下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 02:40:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>日本首相岸田将下台，因丑闻太多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-pm-kishida-wont-run-re-election-ldp-race-kyodo-reports-2024-08-14/</link><description>日本首相岸田文雄表示，他将于九月下台，结束因政治丑闻而受损的三年任期，并为新首相应对物价上涨的影响铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 01:34:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-pm-kishida-wont-run-re-election-ldp-race-kyodo-reports-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国通胀数据良好后美元下跌；新西兰元因降息而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-after-benign-inflation-data-kiwi-firm-before-rbnz-decision-2024-08-14/</link><description>美元兑主要货币隔夜暴跌后，周三仍处于不利地位，因美国生产者价格的良好数据增强了对美联储今年降息的押注。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 00:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-after-benign-inflation-data-kiwi-firm-before-rbnz-decision-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔加拉法、山东队晋级亚冠联赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-gharafa-shandong-secure-berths-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-14/</link><description>卡塔尔的阿尔加拉法队和中国的山东泰山队在周五的新亚冠联赛小组赛抽签中占据了剩余的两个席位，周二的附加赛分别战胜了沙巴布·阿赫利队和曼谷联队。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 00:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-gharafa-shandong-secure-berths-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>加州允许中国机器人出租车公司文远知行进行乘客测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/california-allows-chinese-robotaxi-firm-weride-test-with-passengers-2024-08-13/</link><description>根据加州公用事业监管机构的许可，中国自动驾驶初创公司文远知行已获得加州批准，可以测试其无人驾驶汽车载客。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/california-allows-chinese-robotaxi-firm-weride-test-with-passengers-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示日本8月份商业信心因中国经济放缓而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-business-sentiment-aug-slips-chinas-slowdown-2024-08-13/</link><description>路透短观月度调查周三发现，日本制造商对 8 月份商业状况的信心略有下降，服务业情绪有所缓和，原因是中国需求低迷打压了企业信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-business-sentiment-aug-slips-chinas-slowdown-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：市场摆脱了波动，但这种情况会持续吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-08-13/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 21:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国陆军情报分析师承认向中国出售军事机密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-army-intelligence-analyst-pleads-guilty-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-08-13/</link><description>美国司法部表示，一名美国陆军情报分析员周二承认密谋向中国出售军事机密的指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 21:17:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-army-intelligence-analyst-pleads-guilty-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月新增贷款创15年来新低 预计将出台更多政策措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-new-loans-hit-15-year-low-july-more-policy-steps-expected-2024-08-13/</link><description>受信贷需求不温不火和季节性因素拖累，7月份中国银行贷款降幅超预期，创近15年来最低，并引发人们对央行可能推出更多宽松举措的预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 18:38:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-new-loans-hit-15-year-low-july-more-policy-steps-expected-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，华为准备推出新的人工智能芯片，在中国挑战英伟达</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/huawei-readies-new-ai-chip-challenge-nvidia-china-wsj-reports-2024-08-13/</link><description>《华尔街日报》周二援引消息人士的话报道称，在美国制裁之际，中国华为技术有限公司即将推出一款用于人工智能的新芯片，以在中国挑战英伟达。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/huawei-readies-new-ai-chip-challenge-nvidia-china-wsj-reports-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>什么是人民币套利交易？它与日元有何不同？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/what-is-chinese-yuan-carry-trade-how-is-it-different-yens-2024-08-13/</link><description>日元资助的套利交易平仓引发的全球市场抛售让人民币成为人们关注的焦点，人民币也被广泛用作廉价融资货币。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 04:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/what-is-chinese-yuan-carry-trade-how-is-it-different-yens-2024-08-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>